16:["$","p",null,{"children":"In other words, this is a step forward in detection, not a breakthrough in outcomes. The test’s accuracy in controlled settings doesn’t yet translate to clinical utility, and the harder question—whether earlier detection actually saves lives—remains unanswered."}]
